DESCRIPTION:• discussed 604 and exam.\n  • ☐ HB to propose date in first we
 ek of June *after* Tapiwa meets\n    with Lesser.\n• BTP: deadline mid-May
 \, interviews end of May.  Tapiwa will apply.\n  • HB asked him to circula
 te his personal statement to HB and TE for\n    feedback.\n• ☑ HB to draft
  message to TE re: pause in research work for exams.
